		<div>Different ideas for spell lines was thinking of a good way to maintain our dps in groups what do you all thing of this ??<br />
<br />
Sphere line - similare to ward spells in its damage idea but implemented better can be cast single target similar to cleric revers damage shields places a wall between mobs and group with various effects<br />
<br />
All spells would be dependent on mele strikes after initial casts against group memeber so would not increase solo power no wizard would want to get hit that much <br />
<br />
Fire Sphere - initial cast is a nuke the nuke sets the starting point for the reverse damage shield for example nuke for 800 after that when mobs are hitting mele it will act as a reverse damage shield spell starts at 800 points and is beat off in increments of 200 points so 800 point initial nuke then mob takes fire damage in waves till the damage is used up 800+600+400+200+100 = 2900 total damage<br />
<br />
<br />
Ice Sphere- Initial cast is a nuke the nuke value sets up the spheres total mitigation (ie 1500 point nuke = 1500 sheild against mele attacks) (2000 nuke = 2000 hp mitigation on mele attacks) .Sphere of spiked ice between group and mob ice = 10% damage mitigation bonus to mele in group and 150pt ds against mob + 15% incremental slow as ice wall is beat off mob slow maxes out at 60% slow ?<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
example mob is nuked for 2000 mob hits sphere wall and sphere wall takes 400 points of damage mele behind wall takes 360 mob takes 150point ds and is slowed on hitting the wall first time 15% second hit mob hits the wall for 500 takes 150pts of damage mele takes 450 points of damage mob is slowed 30% wall is hit for 500 pints mele takes 450 mob takes 150point ds and is down to 45% mob hits wall for 500 mele in group is hit for 450 mob takes ds of 150hp and is slowed 60% and wall is gone<br />
<br />
150x5=2750 damage total damage<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
